# Mercur Dev Commands

> All commands run from `C:\Projects\BAW\mercur` unless noted.

---

## 🚀 Starting the Dev Server

### ⚠️ First time OR after a cold restart (node killed)

You must build the framework package first — **always do this after `taskkill` or a fresh clone:**

```powershell
yarn workspace @mercurjs/framework build
yarn dev
```

### Normal restart (server was stopped cleanly with Ctrl+C)

```powershell
yarn dev
```

---

## 🛑 Stopping the Dev Server

### Clean stop (preferred)
Press **`Ctrl + C`** in the terminal running `yarn dev`.

### Force kill all Node processes
```powershell
taskkill /F /IM node.exe
```
> ⚠️ Kills ALL Node.js processes on your machine. After this, always rebuild framework before `yarn dev`.

---

## 🔨 Build Commands

| Command | What it does |
|---|---|
| `yarn workspace @mercurjs/framework build` | Build the shared framework package (required after cold restart) |
| `yarn build` | Build all packages (production build) |
| `yarn workspace api build` | Build only the backend app |
| `yarn workspace @mercurjs/b2c-core build` | Build only the b2c-core plugin |

---

## 🗄️ Database Commands

> Run from `apps/backend`

```powershell
cd apps\backend

yarn db:migrate     # Run all pending migrations
yarn seed           # Seed demo data (products, regions, etc.)
```

---

## 🧹 Lint & Format

```powershell
yarn lint           # Check for lint errors
yarn lint:fix       # Auto-fix lint errors
yarn format         # Format all .ts/.tsx files
yarn format:check   # Check formatting without writing
```

---

## 🧪 Tests

> Run from `apps/backend`

```powershell
cd apps\backend

yarn test:unit                  # Unit tests
yarn test:integration:http      # HTTP integration tests
yarn test:integration:modules   # Module integration tests
```

---

## 📦 Run a Single Package in Dev Mode

```powershell
yarn workspace @mercurjs/b2c-core dev
yarn workspace @mercurjs/commission dev
yarn workspace @mercurjs/reviews dev
yarn workspace @mercurjs/requests dev
yarn workspace @mercurjs/resend dev
yarn workspace @mercurjs/algolia dev
yarn workspace @mercurjs/payment-stripe-connect dev
yarn workspace @mercurjs/stripe-tax-provider dev
yarn workspace api dev
```

---

## 🌐 Ports When Running

| Service | URL |
|---|---|
| Backend API | http://localhost:9000 |
| Health check | http://localhost:9000/health |
| Store API | http://localhost:9000/store/... |
| Vendor API | http://localhost:9000/vendor/... |
| Admin API | http://localhost:9000/admin/... |
